[SN]TITLE[SN]
County Londonderry: Man in critical condition following crash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man is in a critical condition following a crash in Coleraine in County Londonderry.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The one vehicle collision happened on the Curragh Road just after 0630 GMT on Saturday.
He was then taken to hospital.
Diversions are in place between the Bann Road and Coolyvenny Road.
